name: @webpape/ezmax-api-typescript-axios
description: Generated eZmax API with OpenAPI and Typescript/Axios module

scripts.gen: openapi-generator-cli generate -g typescript-axios -t templates -o lib -i ezmax-api-definition.json -c templates/._config.yaml --enable-post-process-file --additional-properties=withSeparateModelsAndApi=true,apiPackage=api,enumPropertyNaming=original,modelPackage=model,supportsES6=true

author: papeweb
